## **1. CLARIFICATIONS NEEDED** *(Design Decisions Required)*

### **CRITICAL PRIORITY** (Blocks Core Implementation)

| ID | Question | Phase | Impact | Suggested Resolution |
|----|----------|-------|--------|---------------------|
| **C1** | **ClosestEnemies Behavior**: Phase 3 says "always one", UI spec says "highlights all". Which is correct? | Phase 3, Phase 4 | Ability implementation | **Recommend:** Hits ONE adjacent (implementation order), highlights ALL for visibility |
| **C2** | **Repair Degradation Floor**: Can mech max HP degrade to 0%? Or is there a minimum? | Phase 2 | Mech balance | **Recommend:** 20% minimum (5 repairs max), prevents infinite degradation |
| **C3** | **ClosestEnemies Failure**: If no adjacent enemies, does ability fail or waste turn? | Phase 3 | Combat flow | **Recommend:** Ability grays out if no valid targets (prevent wasted turns) |

### **HIGH PRIORITY** (Needed Before Beta)

| ID | Question | Phase | Impact | Suggested Resolution |
|----|----------|-------|--------|---------------------|
| **C4** | **Team Container Toggle**: How does player switch between viewing friendly/enemy team? | Phase 4 | UX | **Recommend:** Tab key toggle OR click "Team" label |
| **C5** | **HP Bar Animation**: Should HP changes animate smoothly or snap instantly? | Phase 4 | Visual feedback | **Recommend:** Smooth (0.3s) for clarity, instant for performance mode |
| **C6** | **Queue Update Animation**: When queue reorders, do portraits slide or snap? | Phase 4 | Visual feedback | **Recommend:** Smooth slide (0.2s) for clarity |
| **C7** | **Dead Unit Display**: In team container, are dead units removed, grayed, or marked? | Phase 4 | UX | **Recommend:** Grayed out (preserves composition visibility) |
| **C8** | **Effect Panel Overflow**: If unit has >10 effects, how to display? | Phase 4 | UI | **Recommend:** Compress icons OR show first 10 + "+X more" indicator |

### **MEDIUM PRIORITY** (Nice to Have)

| ID | Question | Phase | Impact | Suggested Resolution |
|----|----------|-------|--------|---------------------|
| **C9** | **Defend Stance + Forced Movement**: If unit in Defend is pushed, which takes priority? | Phase 3 | Edge case | **Recommend:** Push breaks Defend stance (movement > stance) |
| **C10** | **Engineer Mech Restoration Cost**: What does max-level Engineer pay to restore destroyed mech? | Phase 3 | Economy | **Recommend:** High gold cost + materials (balancing decision) |
| **C11** | **Effect Dispel Priority**: When removing multiple effects, which are removed first? | Phase 2 | Priest balancing | **Recommend:** Debuffs before buffs, shortest duration first |
| **C12** | **Same-Effect Magnitude Stacking**: If two different abilities both give "+20% Attack", do they stack? | Phase 2 | Balance clarity | **Answered:** Yes, if from different DataAssets (additive) |

### **LOW PRIORITY** (Post-Launch)

| ID | Question | Phase | Impact | Suggested Resolution |
|----|----------|-------|--------|---------------------|
| **C13** | **Animation Skip Behavior**: Should skip complete current animation or fast-forward? | Phase 3 | QoL | **Recommend:** Jump to end frame (instant completion) |
| **C14** | **Camera Auto-Pan**: Should camera follow acting unit automatically? | Phase 4 | UX preference | **Recommend:** Toggle option (default ON) |
| **C15** | **Salvo Sound Design**: Do all units' sounds overlap or play sequentially? | Phase 3 | Audio polish | **Recommend:** Slight overlap (0.1s offset) for volley feel |

