## **9. RISK ASSESSMENT**

### **High Risk Items**

| Risk | Probability | Impact | Mitigation |
|------|-------------|--------|------------|
| Chain ability system too complex | Medium | High | Start with simple 2-step chains, expand gradually |
| Phylactery bugs with death system | High | Medium | Extensive edge case testing, unit tests |
| Animation blocking causes performance issues | Medium | High | Optimize animation blending, add skip functionality |
| Effect stacking causes balance issues | Low | High | Playtest heavily, adjust per-faction caps |

### **Medium Risk Items**

| Risk | Probability | Impact | Mitigation |
|------|-------------|--------|------------|
| Salvo creates turn order confusion | Medium | Medium | Clear visual feedback, tutorial |
